get info on packages with non-ok status

Source: R/tabulate_states.R
packages_with_events.Rd

get info on packages with non-ok status

packages_with_events(aset)

Arguments

aset

ArtifSet instance

Value

a list with one element per phase in which some package produced non-OK state

Examples

z = make_demo_ArtifSet()
#> starting untar...
#> done.
packages_with_events(z)
